```go
before:
  hooks:
    - go mod tidy
    - go generate ./...
```

```go
builds:
  - env:
    - CGO_ENABLED=0
  goos:
    - linux
    - windows
    - darwin
```

```go
archives:
  - format: tar.gz
    name_template: >-
      {{ .ProjectName }}_
      {{- title .Os }}_
      {{- if eq .Arch "amd64" }}x86_64
      {{- else if eq .Arch "386" }}i386
      {{- else }}{{ .Arch }}{{ end }}
      {{- if .Arm }}v{{ .Arm }}{{ end }}
  format_overrides:
  - goos: windows
    format: zip
```

```go
brews:
  -
  name: audiofile
  homepage: https://github.com/marianina8
  tap:
    owner: marianina8
    name: homebrew-audiofile
  commit_author:
    name: marianina8
```

```go
on:
  push:
    # run only against tags
    tags:
    - '*'
```

```go
permissions:
  contents: write
  # packages: write
  # issues: write
```

```go
jobs:
  goreleaser:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v3
        with:
          fetch-depth: 0
      - run: git fetch --force --tags
      - uses: actions/setup-go@v3
        with:
          go-version: '>=1.20.0'
          cache: true
      - uses: goreleaser/goreleaser-action@v4
        with:
          distribution: goreleaser
          version: latest
          args: release --clean
        env:
          GITHUB_TOKEN: ${{ secrets.GITHUB_TOKEN }}
```
